n Streams Attack on Titan TV Anime|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-04-12/funimation-streams-attack-on-titan-tv-anime|date=2013-04-12|publisher=Anime News Network|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-04-12|archive-date=2018-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206122634/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-04-12/funimation-streams-attack-on-titan-tv-anime}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Crunchyroll to Stream "Attack on Titan" Anime|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2013/04/12/crunchyroll-to-stream-attack-on-titan-anime|date=2013-04-13|publisher=[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-04-13|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403174507/https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2013/04/12/crunchyroll-to-stream-attack-on-Titan-anime}}</ref>。2014年，Funimation授权发行了家庭视频版本<ref>{{cite web|title=Funimation Plans Attack on Titan on Home Video in 2014|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-05-19/funimation-plans-attack-on-titan-on-home-video-in-2014|date=2013-05-19|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-05-21|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412224641/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-05-19/funimation-plans-attack-on-titan-on-home-video-in-2014}}</ref>。本季第一集的英文版在Anime Boston首映<ref>{{cite web|title=Attack on Titan English Dub Premiere at Anime Boston|url=http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/02/14/attack-on-titan-crew-announcement-and-english-dub-info/|date=2014-02-14|publisher=[[Funimation|Funimation]]|language=en|access-date=2014-06-28|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416144950/https://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/02/14/attack-on-titan-crew-announcement-and-english-dub-info/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其他剧集则在Funimation上接受订阅播映<ref>{{cite web|title=FUNimation - Thank you all for your patience! Attack on...|url=https://www.facebook.com/FUNimation/po