== 反响 ==

=== 销量、观看流量 ===
本剧动画在日本非常成功，9卷动画光碟的平均销量为52067份，截至2016年8月，总销量为468603份<ref>{{cite web|title=2000–Present, Average Sales of 10,000 or More|url=http://www.someanithing.com/1|work=someanithing.com|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109063142/http://www.someanithing.com/1|archive-date=2015-11-09|language=en|accessdate=2021-02-11}}</ref>。本片也是2013年日本销量第一的电视動畫<ref>{{cite web|title=年別 > 2013年|url=https://www38.atwiki.jp/uri-archive/pages/176.html|work=38.atwiki.jp|language=ja|access-date=2017-05-17|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109224733/http://www38.atwiki.jp/uri-archive/pages/176.html|archive-date=2016-11-09}}</ref>，甚至直到2017年都还是21世纪最初十年销量前八的动画作品<ref>{{cite web|title=2010年代TVアニメ 累計平均ランキング|url=https://www38.atwiki.jp/uri-archive/pages/251.html|work=38.atwiki.jp|language=ja|access-date=2017-05-17|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024130031/http://www38.atwiki.jp/uri-archive/pages/251.html|archive-date=2016-10-24}}</ref>。在中国大陆，独家引进版权的爱奇艺在第一季播映结束后获得了3.2亿的网络播放量<ref>{{Cite web|title=《进击的巨人》引明星追看 柯震东晒搞怪COS照 - 动漫频道 - 杭州网|url=https://comic.hangzhou.com.cn/dmzx/dmxw/content/2013-10/12/content_4924411.htm|accessdate=2021-02-14|work=comic.hangzhou.com.cn|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214100704/https://comic.hangzhou.com.cn/dmzx/dmxw/content/2013-10/12/content_4924411.htm}}</ref>。本作在北美也非常成功，销售额至少达到20万份<ref>{{cite web|title=The Attack on Titan TV Series Has Sold at Least 200,000 Copies in the U.S.|url=https://animetics.net/2016/12/19/the-attack-on-titan-tv-series-has-sold-at-least-200000-copies-in-the-u-s/|publisher=Animetics|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407234636/https://animetics.net/2016/12/19/the-attack-on-titan-tv-series-has-sold-at-least-200000-copies-in-the-u-s/|archive-date=2017-04-07|language=en|accessdate=2021-02-12}}</ref>。作为2014年Funimation流媒体动画观看量第一名<ref>{{cite web|title=Top FUNimation Streaming Shows of 2014|url=http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/12/26/top-funimation-streaming-shows-of-2014/|work=funimation.com|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910145131/http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/12/26/top-funimation-streaming-shows-of-2014/|archive-date=2015-09-10|language=en|accessdate=2021-02-12}}</ref>，本作同样也是Funimation家庭影视销量的冠军<ref>{{cite web|title=Top Ten Fan Favorite FUNimation Home Video Releases of 2014|url=http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/12/29/top-ten-fan-favorite-funimation-home-video-releases-of-2014/|work=funimation.com|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150909202222/http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/12/29/top-ten-fan-favorite-funimation-home-video-releases-of-2014/|archive-date=2015-09-09|language=en|accessdate=2021-02-12}}</ref>。最终季开播后，其第一集在MyAnimeList上的收视率排名为全剧历代第一，在法国甚至是第三季第一集的14倍之多<ref name=":2" />。

=== 提名和获奖 ===
在第三届[[Newtype_(雜誌)|Newtype]]动画奖上，本剧获得了多个奖项，包括最佳导演、最佳剧本、最佳配乐、最佳主题曲、年度最佳女性角色以及年度动画等<ref>{{cite web|title=Attack on Titan Wins Top Prizes in Newtype Anime Awards – News|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-10-13/attack-on-titan-wins-top-prizes-in-newtype-anime-awards|date=2013-10-13|publisher=Anime News Network|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121103813/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-10-13/attack-on-titan-wins-top-prizes-in-newtype-anime-awards|archive-date=2015-11-21}}</ref>。本片在2013年[[神户动画奖|神户动画奖]]中获得了最佳电视动画奖<ref>{{cite web|title='Attack on Titan,' 'Garden of Words' take top honors at Kobe anime awards|url=http://ajw.asahi.com/article/cool_japan/movies/AJ201312210038|date=2013-12-21|publisher=[[Asahi_Shimbun|Asahi Shimbun]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2014-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721193751/http://ajw.asahi.com/article/cool_japan/movies/AJ201312210038|archive-date=2015-07-21}}</ref>，除此之外还获得了2014年[[东京动画奖|东京动画奖]]的年度动画奖，以及最佳导演、最佳编剧和最佳音乐<ref>{{cite web|title=Announcement of The Tokyo Anime Award Festival 2014 Anime Of The Year Winning Programs And Winners. – TOKYO ANIME AWARD FESTIVAL 2016 – 東京アニメアワードフェスティバル2016|url=http://animefestival.jp/en/post/259/|accessdate=2021-02-12|work=TOKYO ANIME AWARD FESTIVAL 2016 – 東京アニメアワードフェスティバル2016|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526044423/http://animefestival.jp/en/post/259/|archive-date=2015-05-26}}</ref>。在日本第19届年度数字媒体协会（AMD）奖中，本片还获得了2013年度数字内容奖<ref>{{cite web|title=Attack on Titan Wins Digital Contents of the Year Award|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-18/attack-on-titan-wins-digital-contents-of-the-year-award|accessdate=2021-02-12|work=Anime News Network|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819224659/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-18/attack-on-titan-wins-digital-contents-of-the-year-award|archive-date=2015-08-19}}</ref>。2015年的[[SUGOI_JAPAN_Award|SUGOI JAPAN Award]]上，本剧在动画门类获得第7名<ref>{{Cite web|title=「SUGOI JAPAN Award2015」初代グランプリ決定、世界に発信したい作品はこれだ|url=http://ebook.itmedia.co.jp/ebook/articles/1503/13/news045.html|accessdate=2021-02-13|work=ITmedia eBook USER|language=ja|dead-url=no|archive-date=2019-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116153458/http://ebook.itmedia.co.jp/ebook/articles/1503/13/news045.html}}</ref>。而在中国大陆以动漫迷聚集的视频网站[[哔哩哔哩|哔哩哔哩]]，在本剧最终季开播后评选出的“bilibili2020年度动画榜单”上，“年度动画”、“日本续作”、“往年动画”、“年度动画角色”等项的榜首均出自动画《进击的巨人》系列<ref>{{Cite web|title=B站发布2020年度动画榜单 《进击的巨人》最终季人气最高|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-01-16/doc-ikftpnnx8054526.shtml|accessdate=2021-02-13|author=|date=2021-01-16|last=cnBeta|format=|work=finance.sina.com.cn|publisher=|language=zh-cn}}</ref>。
