评价《进击的巨人》前三季动画因故事情节、画面、人物动作、配乐、配音以及黑暗基调而广受好评，不仅在日本国内获得了巨大的影响力，在世界各地也收获了大量的人气<ref>{{cite news|title=The Political Interpretations of Attack on Titan|last=Rezaee|first=Stan|date=2020-12-16|url=https://8bitdigi.com/political-interpretations-of-attack-on-titan/|work=8Bit/Digi|author=|publisher=|accessdate=2021-02-15|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215152939/https://8bitdigi.com/political-interpretations-of-attack-on-titan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年5月27日，香港免费报纸[[am730|am730]]的头版刊登了有关该动画在香港、中国大陆和台湾的流行程度的报道<ref name="am730">{{cite news|url=http://www.am730.com.hk/article.php?article=156271&d=2053|title=《進擊の巨人》爆紅中港台 Youtube點擊400萬 網民熱議圍牆抗敵|work=[[am730|am730]]|date=2013-05-27|access-date=2013-06-27|location=香港|page=1|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607165648/http://www.am730.com.hk/article.php?article=156271&d=2053|archive-date=2013-06-07|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw}}</ref>。本剧也遭到了一些批评，韩国《电子时报》杂志指责本剧带有[[军国主义|军国主义]]色彩，符合时任[[日本首相|日本首相]][[安倍晋三|安倍晋三]]的政治倾向<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/jun/12/today-int7.htm|title=軍國主義復活？／進擊的巨人 引發韓日論戰|work=[[自由时报|自由时报]]|location=台北|date=2013-06-12|access-date=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625080208/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/jun/12/today-int7.htm|archive-date=2013-06-25|dead-url=no|language=zh-tw}}</ref>。[[动画新闻网|动画新闻网]]的卡尔·金姆林格（Carl Kimlinger）批评导演荒木哲郎对本剧最初两集的处理“显然是想让本片看起来强大而令人不安，但它最终只是粗糙而令人不愉快。”<ref>{{cite web|title=The Spring 2013 Anime Preview Guide|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/carl|author=Kimlinger, Carl|date=2013-04-04|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130408093522/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/carl|archive-date=2013-04-08}}</ref>然而，同一网站的其他影评人对该剧大加赞赏。丽贝卡·西尔弗曼（Rebecca Silverman）表示，本片“视觉效果既华丽又让人震撼”，并且“融合了18世纪[[哥特小说|哥特小说家]][[安·拉德克利夫|安·拉德克利夫]]所定义的恐惧与恐怖：一种是物理上的，让人想移开视线，另一种是精神上的，让您想知道接下来会发生什么。”<ref>{{cite web|title=The Spring 2013 Anime Preview Guide|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/rebecca|author=Silverman, Rebecca|date=2013-04-03|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130407042606/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/rebecca|archive-date=2013-04-07}}</ref>卡洛·桑托斯（Carlo Santos）指出，“很少有（末世动作片）能像《进击的巨人》那样完美。”桑托斯只看了第一集就将本片描述为“死亡和毁灭的杰作”<ref>{{cite web|title=The Spring 2013 Anime Preview Guide|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/carlo|author=Santos, Carlo|date=2013-04-04|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130407042601/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/carlo|archive-date=2013-04-07}}</ref>。尽管觉得这部动画有点“{{Le|有限动画|Limited animation|低成本}}”，塞隆·马丁（Theron Martin）还是称赞了本片的配乐以及“紧张而又有感染力的第一集”。马丁还将《进击的巨人》的氛围和视觉美学与[[八木教广|八木教广]]的漫画《[[獵魔戰記|大剑]]》进行了比较<ref>{{cite web|title=The Spring 2013 Anime Preview Guide|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/theron|author=Martin, Theron|date=2013-04-03|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130407042611/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/theron|archive-date=2013-04-07}}</ref>。

DVD Talk的约翰·辛诺特（John Sinnott）称该系列动画是他所看过的最好的系列作品之一，并且是“動畫迷不应该错过的系列”<ref>{{cite web|title=Attack on Titan, Part 1 (Blu-ray)|url=https://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/64121/attack-on-titan-part-1/|author=Sinnott, John|date=2014-06-13|publisher=[[DVD_Talk|DVD Talk]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705185012/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/64121/attack-on-titan-part-1/|archive-date=2017-07-05}}</ref>。身为《[[紐約_(雜誌)|纽约]]》杂志以及vulture.com编辑的玛雅·菲利普斯（Maya Phillips）称赞本剧的独道之处，她说：“在当今令人恐惧的[[反乌托邦|反乌托邦]]现实时代，很难找到有新意的反乌托邦演绎，然而本片做到了。”<ref>{{Cite news|title=The 10 Best Anime Shows on Netflix|work=Vulture|url=https://www.vulture.com/2017/10/best-anime-to-watch-on-netflix.html|date=2017-10-10|language=en|author=Maya Phillips|publisher=|accessdate=2021-02-14|format=|archive-date=2022-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220203162714/https://www.vulture.com/2017/10/best-anime-to-watch-on-netflix.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>至于《[[卫报|卫报]]》的菲利姆·奥尼尔（Phelim O'Neill）称赞该系列的动画作品为“令人陶醉的……杂技极好，而且非常精彩”<ref>{{Cite news|title=Attack on Titan box set review - teens tangle with people-eating giants in this spellbinding anime|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/oct/16/attack-on-titan-box-set-review-manga|date=2014-10-16|language=en|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210215134422/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/oct/16/attack-on-titan-box-set-review-manga|archivedate=2021-02-15|accessdate=2021-02-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。关于动画第三季后半段的高潮部分，Manga.Tokyo称作者谏山创为“天才”，因为他很好地处理了主人公父亲古利夏·葉卡的过去，从而使当前发生的事件与漫画中的故事开头的事件平稳地联系在一起<ref>{{cite web|title=Attack on Titan Episode 57 Review: That Day|url=https://manga.tokyo/anime-review/attack-on-titan-episode-57-review-that-day/|publisher=Manga.Tokyo|language=en|access-date=2019-06-20|archive-date=2021-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210714154529/https://manga.tokyo/anime-review/attack-on-titan-episode-57-review-that-day/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终季第一集上映后就打破了本剧的单集收视纪录，甚至在IMDb上得到了9.4分<ref>{{Cite web|title=《進擊的巨人》最終篇9.8分完美結局！當年動畫化錢作怪險難產？|url=https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/569819/進擊的巨人-最終篇9-8分完美結局-當年動畫化錢作怪險難產|accessdate=2021-02-13|date=2021-01-09|last=影視獨舌|work=香港01|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2021-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210710035406/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/569819/%E9%80%B2%E6%93%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A8%E4%BA%BA-%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82%E7%AF%879-8%E5%88%86%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E5%8C%96%E9%8C%A2%E4%BD%9C%E6%80%AA%E9%9A%AA%E9%9B%A3%E7%94%A2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而据日本媒体统计，最终季在日本海外的收视率创下了历代最高纪录<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=《进击的巨人》TV动画最终季火热 世界人气度达历代最高|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-12-27/doc-iiznezxs9175997.shtml|accessdate=2021-02-13|author=|date=2020-12-27|last=cnBeta|format=|work=finance.sina.com.cn|publisher=|language=zh-cn|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210215155335/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-12-27/doc-iiznezxs9175997.shtml|archivedate=2021-02-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管本剧在中国大陆遭到封禁，但在最终季开播一周内，评分类网站豆瓣网收到的观众对本季综合评分最高时达到9.9分（满分10分），前三季的评分也分别达到了9.4、9.6和9.8分<ref>{{Cite web|title=顶流动漫 进击的巨人上热搜：全部9分+ 第四季罕见9.9 - 日韩漫画|url=http://hot.cnbeta.com/articles/comic/1065461.htm|accessdate=2021-02-15|last=cnBeta|work=cnBeta.COM|language=zh-CN|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210215134206/https://hot.cnbeta.com/articles/comic/1065461.htm|archivedate=2021-02-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Crunchyroll将《进击的巨人》列为“2010年度25大最佳動畫”<ref>{{cite web|title=Crunchyroll Names The Top 100 Anime of the 2010s|url=http://animeuknews.net/2019/11/crunchyroll-names-the-top-100-anime-of-the-2010s/|date=2019-11-27|language=en|dead-url=no|last1=Wolf|first1=Ian|website=Anime UK News|access-date=2020-01-06|archive-date=2019-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191127213200/http://animeuknews.net/2019/11/crunchyroll-names-the-top-100-anime-of-the-2010s/}}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]和[[Polygon|Polygon]]还将《进击的巨人》列为2010年度最佳動畫系列之一<ref>{{cite web|title=The Best Anime of the Decade (2010 - 2019)|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2020/01/01/best-anime-of-the-decade-2010-2019|date=2020-01-01|language=en|dead-url=no|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|access-date=2020-01-06|archive-date=2020-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200101214124/https://www.ign.com/articles/2020/01/01/best-anime-of-the-decade-2010-2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The best anime of the decade|url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/11/6/20948241/best-new-anime-of-the-decade-2010s|date=2019-11-06|language=en|dead-url=no|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|access-date=2020-01-24|archive-date=2019-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220154644/https://www.polygon.com/2019/11/6/20948241/best-new-anime-of-the-decade-2010s}}</ref>。

=== 政治视角解读 ===
该剧引起了部分香港年轻人的关注，他们将剧中城墙内的人理解为香港或者日本，而不断入侵的巨人们则视为是对中国大陆的隐喻<ref name="am7302">{{cite news|url=http://www.am730.com.hk/article.php?article=156271&d=2053|work=[[am730|am730]]|date=2013-05-27|location=Hong Kong|page=1|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607165648/http://www.am730.com.hk/article.php?article=156271&d=2053|archive-date=2013-06-07|title=《進擊の巨人》爆紅中港台 Youtube點擊400萬 網民熱議圍牆抗敵|author=|publisher=|accessdate=2013-06-27|language=zh-hk|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年随着动画的热播，媒体发现原作漫画作者谏山创曾在2010年的博客中表示，剧中角色達特·皮克希斯司令的人物原型是[[大日本帝国陆军|大日本帝国陆军]][[大将|大将]][[秋山好古|秋山好古]]，由此引发网友对此的[[網路論戰|激烈讨论]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=日本华媒：日本右翼污染动漫 惹恼亚洲粉丝|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2014-05-23/140930211549.shtml|accessdate=2021-03-29|author=蒋丰|date=2014-05-23|work=news.sina.com.cn|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2021-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210911185738/https://sax.sina.com.cn/newimpress?rotate_count=48&TIMESTAMP=ktg5ht9u&referral=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fo%2F2014-05-23%2F140930211549.shtml&adunitid=PDPS000000021062&am=%7Bds%3A1600x1000%2Cfv%3A0%2Cov%3ALinux%20x86_64%7D&callback=_sinaads_cbs_onnjx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于秋山好古在战争中的一些行径引发的负面评论使得谏山创的博客备受攻击，甚至使其收到了死亡威胁。日媒称，由于部分评论中有语法错误，这些威胁可能是由非日语母语人士所写<ref>{{cite news|title=A Thousand Death Threats Against a Popular Anime Creator|url=http://kotaku.com/a-thousand-death-threats-against-a-popular-anime-creato-631792221|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703032314/http://kotaku.com/a-thousand-death-threats-against-a-popular-anime-creato-631792221|archive-date=2013-07-03|author=Brian Ashcraft|publisher=|accessdate=2021-02-15|language=en|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。对本剧的批判性解读突出了剧中艾爾迪亞人与现实中[[犹太人|犹太人]]的共同特点，指出他们受到瑪雷人的迫害与犹太人受到[[纳粹德国|纳粹德国]]的迫害类似<ref>{{Cite web|title=Attack on Titan: Fascist and Anti-Semitic? Don't Believe the Propaganda|url=https://collider.com/attack-on-titan-fascist/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2019-06-20|work=Collider|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215152940/https://collider.com/attack-on-titan-fascist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，相反的观点认为，虽然艾爾迪亞人看起来反映了犹太人的境遇，但他们的角色塑造是为了让读者产生同情，而不是被描绘成恶棍<ref>{{cite web|title=Here's What 'Attack on Titan' Would Look Like If It Was Pro-Fascist & Anti-Semitic|url=https://collider.com/attack-on-titan-fascist/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2019-06-20|last=Trumbore|first=Dave|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-url=https://archive.today/20190622000659/http://collider.com/attack-on-titan-fascist/|archive-date=2019-06-22|website=Collider|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Attack on Titan's Criticism of Fascism & Racism Is Far From Subtle|url=https://www.cbr.com/attack-on-titan-criticism-of-fascism-racism/|accessdate=2021-02-15|author=|date=2020-06-21|last=Chowdhury|first=Faiyaz|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200724042634/https://www.cbr.com/attack-on-titan-criticism-of-fascism-racism/|archive-date=2020-07-24|website=CBR|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2018年12月12日至13日在[[耶路撒冷希伯来大学|耶路撒冷希伯来大学]]举行的第14届政治学，国际关系和公共政策国际研究生会议上，因巴尔·平库（Inbar Pincu）将本剧中出现的三道墙与中国的[[长城|长城]]、[[柏林墙|柏林墙]]以及以色列西墙进行了比较，并得出结论说任何形式的隔离墙都不会创造出安全的环境，而只是在制造出一种可能在任何时刻崩溃的虚假安全感<ref>{{Cite conference|url=https://davis.huji.ac.il/sites/default/files/davisinst/files/program.conference.final_.updated.version.november.30.2018.revised.pdf|conference=International Graduate Conference in Political Science, International Relations, and Public Policy|date=2018-12-12|language=en|author=Inbar Pincu|title=The False Security of the Wall: The Perception of Security in ‘Attack on Titan’|accessdate=2021-02-15|format=pdf|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215152916/https://davis.huji.ac.il/sites/default/files/davisinst/files/program.conference.final_.updated.version.november.30.2018.revised.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 中国大陆封禁 ===
2015年，[[中华人民共和国文化部|中国文化部]]要求中国大陆地区各文化相关单位禁止发布包括《进击的巨人》在内的38部动画和漫画作品相关的内容，以“保护年轻人的健康”。这些作品被认为带有暴力、色情、恐怖主义和危害公共道德的场景<ref>{{cite web|title=Forget Attack on Titan - China issues its own attack on anime|url=https://www.scmp.com/comment/blogs/article/1822255/forget-attack-titan-china-issues-its-own-attack-anime|accessdate=2021-02-15|author=|date=2015-06-16|last=Blum|first=Jeremy|format=|work=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]]|publisher=|language=en|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210215130128/https://www.scmp.com/comment/blogs/article/1822255/forget-attack-titan-china-issues-its-own-attack-anime|archivedate=2021-02-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。受其影响，原本定于当年在[[上海国际电影节|上海国际电影节]]上展播的动画电影版也临时取消展映<ref>{{Cite news|date=2015-06-11|url=http://www.asahi.com/articles/ASH6C32F9H6CUHBI00Q.html|title=「進撃の巨人」中国で上映中止　文化省ブラックリストに|publisher=朝日新聞|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2016-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330082031/http://www.asahi.com/articles/ASH6C32F9H6CUHBI00Q.html|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2015-06-11|url=http://www.yomiuri.co.jp/world/20150610-OYT1T50139.html|title=中国・上海映画祭で「進撃の巨人」の上映中止|publisher=読売新聞|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150615002549/http://www.yomiuri.co.jp/world/20150610-OYT1T50139.html|dead-url=yes|language=ja}}</ref>。

